@startuml
title Healthcheck Monitor Sequence
actor Operator
participant Monitor
participant Service
participant IncidentLog

Operator -> Monitor: start monitoring
Monitor -> Service: GET /health
alt healthy
    Service --> Monitor: 200 OK
else unhealthy
    Service --> Monitor: 500 / timeout
    Monitor -> IncidentLog: POST incident
    Monitor -> Operator: alert (console/email)
end
@enduml
